column2: SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, str (p.ra, #, #) as ra, str (p.[dec], #, #) as dec, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMag_z, p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMagErr_z FROM BESTDR9..Galaxy AS p JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id ORDER BY x.up_id
